---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`聯絡我 - ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="預約 Vista Cheng 的諮詢服務，或洽談演講合作。" />
		<style>
            .contact-hero {
                padding: 6rem 1rem 4rem;
                text-align: center;
                background: var(--color-warm-bg);
            }
            .contact-hero h1 { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--color-primary); }
            .contact-hero p { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-secondary); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
            
            .grid-cols {
                display: grid;
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 4rem;
                max-width: 1000px;
                margin: 4rem auto;
                padding: 0 1rem;
            }
            @media (min-width: 768px) {
                .grid-cols { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
            }

            .info-card {
                background: white;
                padding: 2.5rem;
                border-radius: 12px;
                box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
                border: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
            }
            .info-card h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 0; color: var(--color-primary); border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-red); padding-bottom: 0.5rem; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
            .info-item { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: 1.1rem; }
            .info-item strong { display: block; color: var(--gray-dark); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
            .info-item a { color: var(--color-primary); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }
            .info-item a:hover { color: var(--color-red); }

            .cal-embed {
                min-height: 600px;
                background: white;
                border-radius: 12px;
                overflow: hidden;
                box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            }
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
            <section class="contact-hero">
                <h1>聯絡我</h1>
                <p>無論是演講邀約、企業內訓，還是個人諮詢，都歡迎與我聯繫。</p>
            </section>

            <div class="grid-cols">
                <!-- Contact Info -->
                <div class="info-card">
                    <h2>合作洽詢</h2>
                    <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--gray);">
                        如果您有明確的合作意向，建議直接來信，說明您的需求、預算以及預計時程，我將會優先處理。
                    </p>
                    
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <strong>Email</strong>
                        <a href="mailto:vista@VistaCheng.com">vista@VistaCheng.com</a>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <strong>社群媒體</strong>
                        <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
                            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/iamvista" target="_blank">Facebook</a>
                            <span style="color:var(--gray-light)">|</span>
                            <a href="https://www.threads.net/@vista" target="_blank">Threads</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="info-item" style="margin-top: 3rem;">
                        <strong>訂閱電子報</strong>
                        <a href="https://iamvista.substack.com/" target="_blank">Vista 的開外掛週報 &rarr;</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Calendly Embed (Placeholder/Link) -->
                <div class="info-card">
                    <h2>預約諮詢</h2>
                    <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--gray);">
                        想聊聊您的寫作計畫或 AI 導入問題？<br/>
                        歡迎直接預約 30 分鐘的視訊會議。
                    </p>
                    <div style="text-align: center; padding: 3rem 0; background: var(--color-warm-bg); border-radius: 8px;">
                        <a href="https://cal.com/iamvista" target="_blank" style="
                            display: inline-block;
                            padding: 1rem 2rem;
                            background: var(--color-primary);
                            color: white;
                            text-decoration: none;
                            border-radius: 6px;
                            font-weight: bold;
                        ">
                            前往預約時間 (Cal.com) &rarr;
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
